channel.title: RsCalifornia 667/711
channel.description:
Been working on this for awhile now and thought I'd share it with you guys!
Progress:
Completed jad, now had 64 waves :) Pest control base has been started on, bit buggy needs abit more work done Fit pits fully working Slayer is 100% just need to add npc's to slayer tower for tasks. Changed the music system so it plays the correct music in the right region. 100% trade, no more bugs fixed the emotes + loaded new animations :) XP rate is perfected Theiving is 100% Token system ontop of the gold for currency Added big teleport thingy which look's really cool for ice glacors! Fixed bone burying Spirit shield making, Godswords and stuff all work And ALOT MORE!>.<
Working on: Custom pets Real Dungoneering Fixing up the skills Storm of armadyl Mage arena Nomad Sacred clay minigame Clan wars
Media:
[IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/33cxmia.png[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/x22fpy.png[/img]
There is alot more then just those cba with pic's really.
Thanks to everybody that is helping me with this project & first time posters ftw :)?
Would love the support.
